        <Parent_String>carving (processes) [300053149], carving and carving techniques [300186207], subtractive processes and techniques [300229471], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
